#@mesher qhull
#@grid 3dTM
#@diam 0.06
#@perflag 3 0 0 0
oofem.tm.out
Transport subproblem of the coupled SMTM cantilever analysis
nltransienttransportproblem nsteps 12000 rtol 1.e-3 alpha 1. nsmax 2000 contextOutputStep 3000 nmodules 2 profileopt 1 lumpedcapa deltatfunction 2
vtkxml primvars 1 5 tstep_step 100 domain_all
dofman primvars 1 5 tstep_step 100 domain_all
domain 3dMassLatticeTransport
OutputManager tstep_step 10 dofman_all
ncrosssect 1 nmat 1 nbc 1 nic 1 nltf 2
simplecs 1
latticetransmat 1 d 1.e3 k 1.e-17 vis 1.e-3 thetas 0.1 thetar 0.0 a 1.e6 m 0.5 contype 1 ctor 0.001
BoundaryCondition 1 loadTimeFunction 1 prescribedvalue 1.732e6
InitialCondition 1 conditions 1 u 1.732e6
PiecewiseLinFunction 1 nPoints 4 t 4 0. 10. 20. 1200000. f(t) 4 1. 1. 0. 0.
PiecewiseLinFunction 2 nPoints 5 t 5 0. 10. 20. 200. 12000. f(t) 5 1. 1. 1. 20. 20.
#%BEGIN_CHECK%
#LOADLEVEL
##TIME
#%END_CHECK%
